gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Spurs 129, Lakers 115
gameRecap.excerpt: The Spurs defeated the Lakers, 129-115. Devin Vassell recorded a career-high 36 points, along with six rebounds, and three assists for the Spurs, with Keldon Johnson adding 17 points and six assists in the victory. LeBron James tallied 23 points, 14 assists, and seven rebounds for the Lakers in the loss. The Spurs improve to 4-20 in the regular season, while the Lakers fall to 15-11.
